### That's a Wrap!

Thanks to 14,771 people from across 102 countries who made Consensus legendary.

Missed the magic? Meet us in Miami for the next Consensus.

[Register for 2026](https://events.coindesk.com/)

The Super Bowl of Blockchain, the World Cup of Web3.


15k+Attendees

Will gather from over 100 countries to attend Consensus 2025


$4TAUM

Assets managed by the finance giants gathered at Consensus 2024


![](https://consensus-hongkong2025.coindesk.com/images/userfiles/home/home-what-is-consensus.png)

## What is Consensus?

Since 2015, Consensus has been more than an event‚Äìit's the annual gathering of the tribes. It's where the most influential voices in blockchain, Web3, and AI come together to drive innovation forward.

In 2025, Consensus brings its flagship event to Toronto, where the world's first Bitcoin and Ethereum ETFs were born. As North America's third-largest tech ecosystem and second-largest financial hub, Toronto unites global innovation with transformative technology leadership.

Built on CoinDesk's foundation of independent, unbiased journalism, Consensus Toronto will weave together breakthrough technologies, from digital assets to artificial intelligence, fostering the collaborations that define what's next.

Don‚Äôt miss this moment‚Äîjoin us in Toronto.

#### 2025 Speakers

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2015

The first Consensus takes place in a New York City ballroom, welcoming 500 guests, 12 sponsors and a handful of speakers including a young crypto-anarchist by the name of Vitalik Buterin.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2015.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2016

Blockchain tech leaders debate the mystery of Satoshi Nakamoto, scaling and more at Consensus 2016

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2016.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2017

The ICO boom hallmarks Consensus 2017 ‚Äì speakers and attendees alike debate their legality and speculate the future.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2017.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2018

WEN LAMBO? One of the most infamous moments in Consensus history is when BitMEX founder Arthur Hayes rented three Lamborghinis and revved their engines just outside the Consensus doors.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2018.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2019

Consensys founder Joe Lubin bets Bitcoin maxi Jimmy Song $500,000 that Ethereum's decentralized apps would have a non-trivial number of users in five years.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-Consensus-2019.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2020

Bitcoin‚Äôs highly-anticipated third halving event happens mid-panel during 2020‚Äôs virtual Consensus Distributed.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-Consensus-2020.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2021

Binance founder and CEO Changpeng ‚ÄúCZ‚Äù Zhao gave a virtual keynote on the importance of regulatory freedom and competition in the crypto space, stating ‚Äúno one can shut down Bitcoin.‚Äù

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2021.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2022

Consensus returns IRL in Austin, Texas, for its biggest gathering yet. 20,000+ people attend the annual confab in June, unknowingly on the precipice of one of the biggest collapses in crypto history.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2022.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2023

In the midst of crypto‚Äôs darkest winter, 15,000 of the industry‚Äôs most dedicated builders and innovators showed up to discuss the best path forward for crypto, blockchain, and Web3.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2023.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2024

CoinDesk celebrates its 10th annual Consensus in Austin, Texas, featuring talks from presidential candidate RFK Jr. and a16z‚Äôs Chris Dixon, among others.

![](https://d2pasa6bkzkrjd.cloudfront.net/site/consensus2025/images/userfiles/consensus-timeline/Image-consensus-2024.jpg)

Celebrating 10+ Years of Consensus

## 2025

Consensus goes global with events in Toronto and Hong Kong. Join us to be a part of this historic journey.
